## Trigger Tests
# PostToolUse (any tool, after 300s interval) -> activates
# PostToolUse (before 300s since last check) -> does NOT activate (throttled)
# PostToolUse (first call, no timestamp file) -> activates

## Fidelity Tests
# Given 2 unread messages: outputs header with count, up to 5 message previews, footer
# Given 0 unread messages: outputs nothing, exit 0
# Given messaging API down (timeout): outputs nothing, exit 0 (graceful)
# Given empty response: outputs nothing, exit 0
# Updates timestamp file on every check
# Never blocks tool execution — informational only
